<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>App Limit Updated — <%= appName %></title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f13;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }
    .wrapper { max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 0 0 32px; }
    .logo-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.25);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);
      border-radius: 8px; font-size: 18px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .logo-text { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #7dd3fc; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #141420 0%, #0f1a20 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628 0%, #0c2240 50%, #0a1628 100%);
      padding: 48px 40px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.25);
    }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute; top: -40px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 200px; height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14,165,233,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .limit-icon {
      width: 80px; height: 80px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0284c7, #0369a1);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      font-size: 38px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(14,165,233,0.5), 0 0 80px rgba(14,165,233,0.2);
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.5px; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 15px; color: #7dd3fc; line-height: 1.6; }
    .content { padding: 36px 40px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 16px; color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 28px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .greeting strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
    /* Limit comparison card */
    .limit-comparison {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 8px 0 32px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .limit-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .limit-box.old { border-color: rgba(100,116,139,0.3); }
    .limit-box.new { border-color: rgba(14,165,233,0.35); background: rgba(14,165,233,0.06); }
    .limit-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .limit-box.old .limit-label { color: #64748b; }
    .limit-box.new .limit-label { color: #38bdf8; }
    .limit-value {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .limit-box.old .limit-value { color: #475569; }
    .limit-box.new .limit-value { color: #7dd3fc; }
    .limit-desc { font-size: 12px; color: #475569; }
    .limit-box.new .limit-desc { color: #38bdf8; opacity: 0.7; }
    .arrow-divider {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #38bdf8;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    /* Info note */
    .info-box {
      background: rgba(14,165,233,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .info-box p { font-size: 14px; color: #7dd3fc; line-height: 1.7; }
    .cta-wrap { text-align: center; margin: 28px 0 8px; }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0284c7, #0ea5e9);
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(14,165,233,0.4);
    }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(14,165,233,0.15), transparent); margin: 32px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 0 40px 32px; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.8; }
    .footer a { color: #0ea5e9; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo-badge">
        <div class="logo-icon">💬</div>
        <span class="logo-text"><%= appName %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="limit-icon">📊</div>
        <h1>App Limit Updated</h1>
        <p>Your app creation quota has been changed by an administrator.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p class="greeting">
          Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,<br /><br />
          An administrator has updated your <strong><%= appName %></strong> account's 
          <strong style="color:#7dd3fc;">app creation limit</strong>. Here's a summary of the change:
        </p>

        <!-- Limit comparison -->
        <div class="limit-comparison">
          <div class="limit-box old">
            <div class="limit-label">Previous Limit</div>
            <div class="limit-value"><%= oldLimit === null ? '∞' : oldLimit %></div>
            <div class="limit-desc"><%= oldLimit === null ? 'Unlimited apps' : 'apps allowed' %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="arrow-divider">→</div>
          <div class="limit-box new">
            <div class="limit-label">New Limit</div>
            <div class="limit-value"><%= newLimit === null ? '∞' : newLimit %></div>
            <div class="limit-desc"><%= newLimit === null ? 'Unlimited apps' : 'apps allowed' %></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <p>
            ℹ️ &nbsp;Your new limit is now active. You can check your current app count and usage 
            in the dashboard at any time. If you need a higher limit, please contact our support team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-wrap">
          <a class="cta-btn" href="#">View My Apps →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This update was made by a <%= appName %> administrator.<br />
          If you have questions, please <a href="#">contact support</a>.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 8px;">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
